{
  "name": "Healing Wave",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "icons/magic/life/heart-area-circle-red-green.webp",
  "system": {
    "itemKey": "",
    "description": "<p>You release a wave of healing energy in a 3 Space Aura. Make a DC 20 Spell Check.</p><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Each creature of your choice in the area regains 1 HP. </p><p><strong>Success:</strong> Each creature of your choice regains 2 HP. </p><p><strong>Success (Each 5):</strong> +1 HP.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Spell Enhancements</span></strong></span></p><p><strong>Area: (1 MP, Repeatable) </strong>The radius of the Aura increases by 2 Spaces.</p><p><strong>Increased Healing: (X MP)</strong> The targets regain +X HP.</p><p><strong>Aura of Healing: (1 MP, Sustained)</strong> The duration of the Spell becomes 1 minute. For the duration, when a creature of your choice ends their turn in the area (including yourself), it can spend a number of Rest Points up to their Prime Modifier, regaining 1 HP per Rest Point spent.</p><p><strong>Rejuvenation: (1 MP, Requires Aura of Healing)</strong> When a creature spends Rest Points on Aura of Healing, they can repeat a Save against an effect they’re subjected to.</p>",
